| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0764 — Recovery Inhibition (kraken)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ff9253e-0d0f-52eb-81a5-b087eee4c58c"
